{
"#name"
:
{
"eget"
:
null
,
"en"
:
"Download and install binaries from GitHub/GitLab/Codeberg Releases"
,
"cn"
:
"从 GitHub/GitLab/Codeberg Release 下载并安装二进制文件"
}
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Download and install pre-built binaries from GitHub/GitLab/Codeberg Releases (Inspired by zyedidia/eget); `x eget use <name>` installs to ~/.local/bin in one step, and for well-known projects a bare name (e.g. `x eget use jq`) is auto-completed to the source repo via the x install database; supports GHPROXY for accelerating GitHub downloads."
,
"cn"
:
"从 GitHub/GitLab/Codeberg Release 下载并安装预编译二进制文件（Inspired by zyedidia/eget）；`x eget use <name>` 一键安装到 ~/.local/bin，对知名项目支持裸名（如 `x eget use jq`），由 x install 数据库补全源作者仓库；支持通过 GHPROXY 加速 GitHub 下载。"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"纯 shell 重新实现，100% 兼容 zyedidia/eget CLI（inactive）。MIT License。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Pure shell reimplementation, 100% compatible with zyedidia/eget CLI (inactive). MIT License.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"推荐用法：`x eget use [owner/]<repo>` —— 从官方 Release 下载并安装到 ~/.local/bin（x-cmd 会自动把 ~/.local/bin 加入 PATH）。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Recommended: `x eget use [owner/]<repo>` — downloads from the official Release and installs to ~/.local/bin (x-cmd automatically adds ~/.local/bin to PATH).\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"裸名补全（如 `x eget use jq` → jqlang/jq）的数据来自 x install 数据库。\n这个数据库只为方便把常用项目名映射到源作者仓库而存在，**不构成对项目本身的推荐或安全审查** —— 安装前请自行判断可信度。\n详见 https://x-cmd.com/install，或 `x i` 交互查看。\n如果你是项目作者，想让自己的项目进入数据库，可参考 https://x-cmd.com/install/submit。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Bare-name completion (e.g. `x eget use jq` → jqlang/jq) is powered by the x install database.\nThe database exists purely to map common project names to their source repos for convenience — it is **NOT a recommendation or security vetting** of the projects themselves. Judge trustworthiness before installing.\nSee https://x-cmd.com/install, or run `x i` for interactive browsing.\nIf you are the project author and want your project included in the database, see https://x-cmd.com/install/submit.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"多平台支持：GitHub、GitLab、Codeberg。短名 gh:/gl:/cb: 快速指定平台。\n例如 x eget gl:owner/repo 从 GitLab 下载。暂不支持 Gitee（Release 下载需登录）。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Multi-forge support: GitHub, GitLab, Codeberg. Use short names gh:/gl:/cb: to specify.\ne.g., x eget gl:owner/repo downloads from GitLab. Gitee not supported (requires login).\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"x eget 直接从作者仓库下载，可按需获取所有版本。x pkg 是 x-cmd 官方打包维护的稳定发行渠道，只引入经过验证的稳定版本。\n"
,
"en"
:
"x eget downloads directly from the author's repo — all versions available on demand. x pkg is x-cmd's curated stable channel, only shipping vetted releases.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"开发者按规范打包并发布到 Release，用户通过 x eget 即下即用，通过 x eget snap 即下即运行。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Developers package and publish to releases following naming conventions, users download instantly with x eget and run instantly with x eget snap.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"GitHub 下载默认带 SHA-256 校验（hash 来自 api.github.com Release asset 的 digest 字段，直连取得）。\n使用 GHPROXY 时尤为重要 —— 代理只截获 github.com 上的二进制下载，无法影响 api.github.com 上的 digest 值，篡改会被立刻发现。\nGitLab / Codeberg release API 无 digest 字段，这两条链路静默跳过校验。可用 --no-verify 关闭。\n"
,
"en"
:
"GitHub downloads are integrity-checked by default (hash from the api.github.com Release asset digest field, fetched directly).\nEspecially important with GHPROXY — the proxy can only intercept github.com binary downloads, never the digest value on api.github.com, so tampering is detected immediately.\nGitLab / Codeberg release APIs have no digest field, so verification is silently skipped for those forges. Disable with --no-verify.\n"
}
]
,
"#tip:note"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"环境变量 `___X_CMD_GHPROXY_ENDPOINT`：GitHub 直连慢时走代理。仅作用于 github.com 资源下载，不影响 api.github.com 与其它 forge（gitlab / codeberg）。\n支持两种写法，自动识别：\n  - 前缀型：`___X_CMD_GHPROXY_ENDPOINT=\"https://your-proxy.example.com\"`         => https://your-proxy.example.com/https://github.com/...\n  - 替换型：`___X_CMD_GHPROXY_ENDPOINT=\"https://your-proxy.example.com/github.com\"` => https://your-proxy.example.com/github.com/...\n末尾斜杠两种模式都会自动去掉。设置后 `x eget` / `x eget snap` 的下载链路均生效；下载日志会打印 `Using GHPROXY: ...` 提示。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Env `___X_CMD_GHPROXY_ENDPOINT`: route slow GitHub downloads through a proxy. Applies only to github.com asset downloads — api.github.com and other forges (gitlab / codeberg) are unaffected.\nTwo endpoint shapes are auto-detected:\n  - prefix:  `___X_CMD_GHPROXY_ENDPOINT=\"https://your-proxy.example.com\"`         => https://your-proxy.example.com/https://github.com/...\n  - replace: `___X_CMD_GHPROXY_ENDPOINT=\"https://your-proxy.example.com/github.com\"` => https://your-proxy.example.com/github.com/...\nTrailing slashes are normalized. Once set, both `x eget` and `x eget snap` are affected; download log prints `Using GHPROXY: ...`.\n"
}
]
,
