"cmd"
:
"x eget unuse rg"
,
"cn"
:
"移除 rg"
,
"en"
:
"Remove rg"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget unuse BurntSushi/ripgrep"
,
"cn"
:
"按全名移除"
,
"en"
:
"Remove by owner/repo"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget unuse --all"
,
"cn"
:
"移除所有"
,
"en"
:
"Remove all"
}
]
}
,
"usels"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"列出所有 use 安装的记录（owner/repo 与 binary 名），TSV 格式带表头"
,
"en"
:
"List all use-installed records (owner/repo and binary name), TSV with header"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget usels"
,
"cn"
:
"列出全部安装记录"
,
"en"
:
"List all installation records"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget usels | tail -n +2 | wc -l"
,
"cn"
:
"统计安装条数（跳过表头）"
,
"en"
:
"Count installations (skip header)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget usels | grep ripgrep"
,
"cn"
:
"过滤特定仓库"
,
"en"
:
"Filter to a specific repo"
}
]
}
,
"upgrade"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"把 use 装的 binary 刷新到最新 release（默认走 snap cache，重复 use 是不会自动升级的）"
,
"en"
:
"Refresh use-installed binaries to their latest release (snap cache means repeated 'use' won't auto-upgrade)"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x eget upgrade <name>"
:
null
}
,
{
"x eget upgrade --all"
:
null
}
,
{
"x eget upgrade --dry-run [--all | <name>]"
:
null
}
]
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"`x eget use <name>` 不会自动检查升级 —— 首次安装后，重复调用永远走 snap cache，0 网络。\n想拿到最新版本必须显式调用 `x eget upgrade`。\n裸 `x eget upgrade`（无参数、无 --all）会报错以避免误触 —— 要么指定名字，要么显式 --all。\n"
,
"en"
:
"`x eget use <name>` does NOT auto-check for upgrades — after the first install, repeated calls always hit the snap cache with zero network.\nTo get the latest release you must explicitly run `x eget upgrade`.\nBare `x eget upgrade` (no args, no --all) errors out to avoid footguns — pass either a name or --all.\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget upgrade --dry-run --all"
,
"cn"
:
"预览所有可升级的 binary（不改文件）"
,
"en"
:
"Preview all upgradable binaries (no filesystem changes)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget upgrade --all"
,
"cn"
:
"升级所有 use 装的 binary"
,
"en"
:
"Upgrade every use-tracked binary"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget upgrade fzf"
,
"cn"
:
"只升级匹配名字或 owner/repo 的 binary"
,
"en"
:
"Upgrade only entries matching by binname or owner/repo"
}
]
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"名字或 owner/repo（按 binname 精确匹配，否则按 owner/repo 子串匹配）"
,
"en"
:
"Name or owner/repo (exact match on binname, otherwise substring match on owner/repo)"
}
}
,
"--all"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"升级 use 跟踪的所有 binary"
,
"en"
:
"Upgrade every use-tracked binary"
}
}
,
"--dry-run"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"只打印 current→latest 对比，不下载、不替换文件"
,
"en"
:
"Print current→latest comparison only; do not download or replace files"
}
}
}
,
"which"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"查找 snap 缓存的 binary 完整路径（不解压、不下载，仅返回已缓存版本）"
,
"en"
:
"Find the full path of a snap-cached binary (no extract, no download — just returns the cached path)"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x eget which [owner/]<repo>"
:
null
}
,
{
"x eget which [owner/]<repo>"
:
null
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget which BurntSushi/ripgrep"
,
"cn"
:
"按 owner/repo 查找缓存路径"
,
"en"
:
"Look up cache path by owner/repo"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget which rg"
,
"cn"
:
"按裸名查找（自动通过 x install 反查 owner）"
,
"en"
:
"Look up by bare name (owner auto-resolved via x install)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget which gh:cli/cli"
,
"cn"
:
"用短名指定 forge"
,
"en"
:
"Specify forge with short prefix"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget which BurntSushi/ripgrep"
,
"cn"
:
"按 owner/repo 查找缓存路径"
,
"en"
:
"Look up cache path by owner/repo"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget which rg"
,
"cn"
:
"按裸名查找（自动通过 x install 反查 owner）"
,
"en"
:
"Look up by bare name (owner auto-resolved via x install)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget which gh:cli/cli"
,
"cn"
:
"用短名指定 forge"
,
"en"
:
"Specify forge with short prefix"
}
]
}
,
"ls"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"不带参数时，列出 x install 数据库中所有可用 eget 安装的包；带参数时，列出仓库的 release 版本或指定版本的 artifact"
,
"en"
:
"Without args, list all eget-installable packages from the x install database; with a repo, list its releases or a specific release's artifacts"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x eget ls [OPTIONS]"
:
null
}
,
{
"x eget ls [OPTIONS] <repo> [<release>]"
:
null
}
]
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"无参数调用 `x eget ls` 会从 `x install --ls --tsv` 中筛选 rule 列含 `/eget` 的条目，输出 NAME / REPO / DESCRIPTION 三列 TSV。\n数据量较大（约 800+ 行），适合管道处理：`x eget ls | grep ripgrep`、`x eget ls | head`、`x eget ls | fzf`。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Calling `x eget ls` with no args filters the x install TSV for rows whose rule column contains `/eget`, emitting a 3-column TSV: NAME / REPO / DESCRIPTION.\nThe list is large (~800 entries) and pipe-friendly: `x eget ls | grep ripgrep`, `x eget ls | head`, `x eget ls | fzf`.\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget ls"
,
"cn"
:
"列出所有可用 eget 安装的包（来自 x install）"
,
"en"
:
"List all eget-installable packages (from x install)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget ls | grep ripgrep"
,
"cn"
:
"过滤特定关键词"
,
"en"
:
"Filter by keyword"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget ls BurntSushi/ripgrep"
,
"cn"
:
"列出仓库的所有 release 版本"
,
"en"
:
"List all releases of a repo"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget ls BurntSushi/ripgrep 14.1.0"
,
"cn"
:
"列出指定 release 的 artifact"
,
"en"
:
"List artifacts in a specific release"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget ls gl:owner/repo"
,
"cn"
:
"列出 GitLab 仓库的 release"
,
"en"
:
"List GitLab releases"
}
]
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"仓库（user/repo 或 gh:/gl:/cb: 短名）"
,
"en"
:
"Repository (user/repo or gh:/gl:/cb: short name)"
}
}
,
"#2"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"指定版本标签（省略则列出所有版本）"
,
"en"
:
"Release tag (omit to list all releases)"
}
}
,
"--forge"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"指定平台"
,
"en"
:
"Specify forge"
}
}
,
"--limit"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"最大列出版本数（默认 20）"
,
"en"
:
"Max releases to list (default 20)"
}
}
,
"--no-ccmd"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"跳过缓存，强制重新请求 API"
,
"en"
:
"Skip cache, force fresh API request"
}
}
}
,
"resolve"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"解析匹配结果，不下载（显示选中的 artifact、URL、版本）"
,
"en"
:
"Resolve best matching asset without downloading"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget resolve BurntSushi/ripgrep"
,
"cn"
:
"预览匹配结果"
,
"en"
:
"Preview match result"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget resolve --system linux/amd64 cli/cli"
,
"cn"
:
"预览指定平台的匹配"
,
"en"
:
"Preview match for a specific platform"
}
]
}
,
"extract"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"从本地压缩包中提取 binary"
,
"en"
:
"Extract binary from a local archive"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x eget extract [OPTIONS] <archive>"
:
null
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget extract ./rg-14.1.0.tar.gz"
,
"cn"
:
"解压到当前目录"
,
"en"
:
"Extract to the current directory"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget extract --to /usr/local/bin ./rg-14.1.0.tar.gz"
,
"cn"
:
"解压到指定目录"
,
"en"
:
"Extract to a specific directory"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget extract -f 'rg*' ./archive.tar.gz"
,
"cn"
:
"按文件名 glob 提取某个文件"
,
"en"
:
"Extract a specific file via name glob"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget extract --all ./archive.tar.gz"
,
"cn"
:
"解压全部内容"
,
"en"
:
"Extract everything in the archive"
}
]
}
,
"cache"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"统一管理 eget 缓存（原始归档 + 抽取后的 snap binary）"
,
"en"
:
"Unified management of eget caches (raw archives + extracted snap binaries)"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x eget cache [OPERATION]"
:
null
}
]
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"eget 维护两套缓存：\n  - `cache/<owner>--<repo>/<version>/<asset>` —— 原始下载的归档包，带 SHA-256 校验。\n  - `snap/<owner>--<repo>/<version>/bin/<binary>` —— 抽取后可直接执行的 binary。\n`snap` / `use` / `upgrade` 全部走 snap 缓存；`download` 默认归档。\n"
,
"en"
:
"eget keeps two caches:\n  - `cache/<owner>--<repo>/<version>/<asset>` — raw downloaded archive, SHA-256 verified.\n  - `snap/<owner>--<repo>/<version>/bin/<binary>` — extracted ready-to-run binary.\n`snap` / `use` / `upgrade` all share the snap cache; `download` defaults to the archive cache.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"`clear` 对两类缓存采用不同策略：归档每仓库保留 N 个版本（默认 5）；snap 只保留 `.default-version`（当前 active 版本），其它版本视为过期。\nsnap 默认版本被 `clear` 保护 —— 想彻底清掉需要 `rm <owner/repo>` 或 `purge`。\n"
,
"en"
:
"`clear` uses different policies: archive keeps N versions per repo (default 5); snap keeps only `.default-version` (the active binary).\nThe snap default version is protected by `clear` — to wipe it, use `rm <owner/repo>` or `purge`.\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget cache ls"
,
"cn"
:
"列出所有缓存条目（带 KIND / REPO / VERSION / BYTES 列）"
,
"en"
:
"List all cache entries (with KIND / REPO / VERSION / BYTES columns)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget cache info"
,
"cn"
:
"显示三类缓存（归档 / snap / use 列表）的路径与占用"
,
"en"
:
"Show path and size of the three caches (archive / snap / use list)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget cache clear 5"
,
"cn"
:
"清理：归档每仓库保留 5 个版本，snap 仅保留 .default-version"
,
"en"
:
"Clear: archive keeps 5 versions per repo; snap keeps .default-version only"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget cache rm jqlang/jq"
,
"cn"
:
"删除某仓库的归档 + snap 缓存"
,
"en"
:
"Remove a repo's archive + snap cache"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget cache rm https://github.com/jqlang/jq"
,
"cn"
:
"用 URL 删除（与 owner/repo 等价）"
,
"en"
:
"Remove by URL (equivalent to owner/repo)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget cache purge"
,
"cn"
:
"全部清空（不可恢复）"
,
"en"
:
"Purge everything (irreversible)"
}
]
}
,
"cache-ls"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"列出 archive + snap 缓存条目（TSV：KIND / REPO / VERSION / BYTES / PATH）"
,
"en"
:
"List archive + snap cache entries (TSV: KIND / REPO / VERSION / BYTES / PATH)"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x eget cache ls"
:
null
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget cache ls"
,
"cn"
:
"列出所有缓存条目"
,
"en"
:
"List all cache entries"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget cache ls | head"
,
"cn"
:
"只看前面几条"
,
"en"
:
"Show first few entries"
}
]
}
,
"cache-info"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"显示三类缓存的路径与大小"
,
"en"
:
"Show path and size of the three caches"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x eget cache info"
:
null
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget cache info"
,
"cn"
:
"显示 archive / snap / use 列表的路径与占用"
,
"en"
:
"Show path and size of archive / snap / use list"
}
]
}
,
"cache-clear"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"清理旧版本（归档每仓库保留 N 个，默认 5；snap 保留 .default-version）"
,
"en"
:
"Prune old versions (archive keeps N per repo, default 5; snap keeps .default-version)"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x eget cache clear [N]"
:
null
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget cache clear 5"
,
"cn"
:
"清理：归档每仓库保留 5 个版本，snap 仅保留 .default-version"
,
"en"
:
"Clear: archive keeps 5 versions per repo; snap keeps .default-version only"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget cache clear 0"
,
"cn"
:
"移除所有归档，snap 仅保留 .default-version"
,
"en"
:
"Remove all archives, snap keeps .default-version only"
}
]
}
,
"cache-purge"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"清空全部缓存（不可恢复）"
,
"en"
:
"Wipe both caches (irreversible)"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x eget cache purge"
:
null
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget cache purge"
,
"cn"
:
"全部清空（不可恢复，下次 use/snap 会重新下载）"
,
"en"
:
"Purge everything (irreversible; next use/snap re-downloads)"
}
]
}
,
"cache-rm"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"删除某仓库的归档 + snap 缓存"
,
"en"
:
"Remove a single repo from both caches"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x eget cache rm <target>"
:
null
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget cache rm jqlang/jq"
,
"cn"
:
"用 owner/repo 删除"
,
"en"
:
"Remove by owner/repo"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget cache rm https://github.com/jqlang/jq"
,
"cn"
:
"用 URL 删除（与 owner/repo 等价）"
,
"en"
:
"Remove by URL (equivalent to owner/repo)"
}
]
}
,
"rate"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"查看 GitHub API 速率限制"
,
"en"
:
"Show GitHub API rate limit"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x eget rate"
:
null
}
]
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"目前只支持 GitHub —— api.github.com 提供 /rate_limit 端点返回剩余配额。\nGitLab / Codeberg 只在每个 API 响应头里报告 rate limit，没有可独立查询的端点，因此暂不支持。\n速率数据基于 EGET_GITHUB_TOKEN / GITHUB_TOKEN 鉴权。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Only GitHub is supported — api.github.com provides a /rate_limit endpoint returning remaining quota.\nGitLab / Codeberg only report rate limit via per-response HTTP headers, with no standalone query endpoint, so they are unsupported.\nAuthenticated via EGET_GITHUB_TOKEN / GITHUB_TOKEN.\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget rate"
,
"cn"
:
"查看 GitHub API 速率限制（剩余 / 上限 / 重置时间）"
,
"en"
:
"Show GitHub API rate limit (remaining / limit / reset time)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x eget rate gh"
,
"cn"
:
"短名等价于默认 github"
,
"en"
:
"Short name equivalent to the default github"
}
]
}
}

